msgid "[^8]: You don't need to trust me, the command to reproduce the stats is `git diff release-3.4.0..release-3.6.0 --shortstat -w -G'(^[^\\*# /])|(^#\\w)|(^\\s+[^\\*#/])' -- '*.c' '*.h' '*.cpp' '*.xml.in' '*.xsl' '*CMakeLists.txt' '*.cl'`"
msgstr "[^8]: Non devi fidarti di me, il comando per riprodurre le statistiche è `git diff release-3.4.0..release-3.6.0 --shortstat -w -G'(^[^\\*# /])|(^#\\w)|(^\\s+[^\\*#/])' -- '*.c' '*.h' '*.cpp' '*.xml.in' '*.xsl' '*CMakeLists.txt' '*.cl'`"

