# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Title ###
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Developer documentation"
msgstr "Documentazione per sviluppatori"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The dev docs are [automatically built](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel/blob/master/.github/workflows/docs.yml) from the source code with Doxygen, every Sunday at 00:00 UTC, then uploaded to <https://dev.ansel.photos>, which is hosted on Github Pages attached to the Ansel (software) repository.\n"
msgstr "La documentazione per sviluppatori viene [generata automaticamente](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel/blob/master/.github/workflows/docs.yml) dal codice sorgente con Doxygen, ogni domenica alle 00:00 UTC, e poi caricata su <https://dev.ansel.photos>, che è ospitata su Github Pages collegate al repository di Ansel (software).\n"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Title ###
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Commits and issues"
msgstr "Commit e issue"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "Github new commits and issues are [automatically posted](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel/blob/master/.github/workflows/matrix.yml) to a [Matrix channel](https://matrix.to/#/#ansel-dev:matrix.org) for updates.\n"
msgstr "I nuovi commit e le nuove issue su Github vengono [pubblicati automaticamente](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel/blob/master/.github/workflows/matrix.yml) su un [canale Matrix](https://matrix.to/#/#ansel-dev:matrix.org) per gli aggiornamenti.\n"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Title ###
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:31
#: content/contribute/organization.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "Website"
msgstr "Sito web"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Hugo static website is [automatically built](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel-website/blob/master/.github/workflows/hugo.yml) on every new commit to the source code and ever Sunday at 00:00 UTC. This auto-update is intended for [camera support](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel-website/blob/master/themes/ansel/layouts/shortcodes/rawspeed.html) which re-parses Libraw, Rawspeed and Ansel source code straight from Github, and dynamically generates the camera support table. It is uploaded to <https://ansel.photos>, which is hosted on Github Pages attached te the Ansel Website repository.\n"
msgstr "Il sito web statico realizzato con Hugo viene [generato automaticamente](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel-website/blob/master/.github/workflows/hugo.yml) a ogni nuovo commit nel codice sorgente e ogni domenica alle 00:00 UTC. Questo aggiornamento automatico è pensato per il [supporto delle fotocamere](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel-website/blob/master/themes/ansel/layouts/shortcodes/rawspeed.html), che ripassa il codice sorgente di Libraw, Rawspeed e Ansel direttamente da Github, e genera dinamicamente la tabella di supporto delle fotocamere. Viene caricato su <https://ansel.photos>, che è ospitato su Github Pages collegate al repository del sito web di Ansel.\n"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Title ###
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:35
#: content/contribute/organization.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "Documentazione"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "The documentation is imported into the website as a Go/Git module ([see _website_](./website/index.md)). Every new commit to the documentation [fires a workflow dispatch](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel-doc/blob/master/.github/workflows/hugo.yml) to the main website to rebuild and update it.\n"
msgstr "La documentazione viene importata nel sito web come modulo Go/Git ([vedi _sito web_](./website/index.md)). Ogni nuovo commit alla documentazione [attiva un workflow dispatch](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel-doc/blob/master/.github/workflows/hugo.yml) verso il sito web principale per rigenerarlo e aggiornarlo.\n"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Title ##
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Forum"
msgstr "Forum"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "New posts on the forum are posted through an RSS bot to the [Matrix channel](https://matrix.to/#/#ansel-dev:matrix.org) for updates.\n"
msgstr "I nuovi post sul forum vengono pubblicati tramite un bot RSS sul [canale Matrix](https://matrix.to/#/#ansel-dev:matrix.org) per gli aggiornamenti.\n"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Title ##
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "Chantal"
msgstr "Chantal"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/contribute/workflows.md:46
#, no-wrap
